{"tid":2130852,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"41歲韓國性感icon李孝利公開20年舊照獲網民讚唔識老：是凍齡女神","createTime":"2020-07-29T12:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T12:37:22.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1f2a33285d4ae150f1a626efe1eecf72aaee1bc","tid":2130852,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:33:29.000Z","msg":"現年41歲的韓國女星李孝利是一代性感icon，無論樣貌和身材多年來都keep得好好。她近日與天王Rain以及「國民MC」劉在錫組成夏日限定混聲組合「SSAK 3」再度人氣急升，成為熱話。她最近亦不時更新IG與粉絲和網民分享生活點滴，呢日她就公開了自己20年前的與粉絲在家門前影的舊照。<br />\n<br />\n李孝利於她的IG公開了她20年前與粉絲的合照，並留言表示：「20年前跟fans在家門前，不知道他們現在在哪裏，正在做甚麼呢？不知道他們覺得我現在怎樣呢？大家現在怎樣了？」她這張照片曝光後，即獲網民大讚她的樣子基乎無老過，現在她的樣子就跟20年前差不多，絕對是個凍齡女神。"},{"pid":"b81d7a6709c2a4b246c8205739e302d2b8f74a4d","tid":2130852,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:33:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200729/365174720712282112.jpeg/09e-l78BdMdEWVf9O0tZlqUMoVbVZDP2sx63JLMetyQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200729%2F365174720712282112.jpeg%2F09e-l78BdMdEWVf9O0tZlqUMoVbVZDP2sx63JLMetyQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=3722dd8b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec9f831672b75018b0d58e65595ead1c3a7cfa44","tid":2130852,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200728/364784021902856192.jpeg/9kDZ0X5fdzj4DQygTDyUs_eeLilCPjPVGhjyYhoY8mI?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200728%2F364784021902856192.jpeg%2F9kDZ0X5fdzj4DQygTDyUs_eeLilCPjPVGhjyYhoY8mI%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1c47673b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200728/364784017041657856.jpeg/N3n7tyMAjRkZN_zm-_YIBFVw7FYI7J0HIGMy5SBjMuU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200728%2